{"id":943,"parent_id":942,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":943,"title":"Zephaniah 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"Zeph.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1","content":[["div",[".title",["span.dominant","Zephaniah"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","The destruction of Judah is symbolic of the Second Coming—It is the day of the Lord’s sacrifice, a day of wrath and trouble."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.1","order":"02.37.001.62428"},["b","1"],"The word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"which came unto Zephaniah the son of Cushi, the son of Gedaliah, the son of Amariah, the son of Hizkiah, in the days of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Josiah"],"the son of Amon, king of Judah."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.2","order":"02.37.001.62429"},["b","2"],"I will utterly",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"consume"],"all",["i","things"],"from off the land, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.3","order":"02.37.001.62430"},["b","3"],"I will consume man and beast; I will consume the fowls of the heaven, and the fishes of the sea, and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"stumblingblocks"],"with the wicked; and I will cut off man from off the land, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.4","order":"02.37.001.62431"},["b","4"],"I will also",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"stretch"],"out mine hand upon Judah, and upon all the inhabitants of Jerusalem; and I will cut off the remnant of Baal from this place,",["i","and"],"the name of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"Chemarims"],"with the priests;"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.5","order":"02.37.001.62432"},["b","5"],"And them that worship the host of heaven upon the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"housetops"],"; and them that worship",["i","and"],"that swear by the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and that swear by",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"Malcham"],";"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.6","order":"02.37.001.62433"},["b","6"],"And them that are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"turned"],"back from the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; and",["i","those"],"that have not sought the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", nor inquired for him."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.7","order":"02.37.001.62434"},["b","7"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Hold"],"thy peace at the presence of the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],": for the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"day"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"at hand: for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath prepared a sacrifice, he hath bid his guests."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.8","order":"02.37.001.62435"},["b","8"],"And it shall come to pass in the day of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s sacrifice, that I will punish the princes, and the king’s children, and all such as are clothed with strange",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"apparel"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.9","order":"02.37.001.62436"},["b","9"],"In the same day also will I punish all those that leap",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"on"],"the threshold, which fill their masters’ houses with violence and deceit."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.10","order":"02.37.001.62437"},["b","10"],"And it shall come to pass in that day, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],",",["i","that there shall be"],"the noise of a cry from the fish",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"gate"],", and an howling from",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"the second"],", and a great crashing from the hills."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.11","order":"02.37.001.62438"},["b","11"],"Howl, ye inhabitants of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Maktesh"],", for all the merchant people are cut down; all they that bear silver are cut off."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.12","order":"02.37.001.62439"},["b","12"],"And it shall come to pass at that time,",["i","that"],"I will search Jerusalem with candles, and punish the men that are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"settled"],"on their",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"lees"],": that say in their heart, The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"will",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"not"],"do good, neither will he do evil."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.13","order":"02.37.001.62440"},["b","13"],"Therefore their goods shall become a booty, and their houses a desolation: they shall also",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"build"],"houses, but not inhabit",["i","them;"],"and they shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"plant"],"vineyards, but not drink the wine thereof."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.14","order":"02.37.001.62441"},["b","14"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"great day"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"near,",["i","it is"],"near, and hasteth greatly,",["i","even"],"the voice of the day of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": the mighty man shall cry there bitterly."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.15","order":"02.37.001.62442"},["b","15"],"That day",["i","is"],"a day of wrath, a day of trouble and distress, a day of wasteness and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"desolation"],", a day of darkness and gloominess, a day of clouds and thick darkness,"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.16","order":"02.37.001.62443"},["b","16"],"A day of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"trumpet"],"and alarm against the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"fenced cities"],", and against the high towers."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.17","order":"02.37.001.62444"},["b","17"],"And I will bring distress upon men, that they shall walk like blind men, because they have sinned against the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": and their blood shall be poured out as dust, and their flesh as the dung."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.18","order":"02.37.001.62445"},["b","18"],"Neither their silver nor their gold shall be able to deliver them in the day of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s wrath; but the whole land shall be devoured by the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"fire"],"of his jealousy: for he shall make even a speedy riddance of all them that dwell in the land."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.1a","order":"02.37.001.62446"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.24"},"2 Kgs. 21:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.2a","order":"02.37.001.62448"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.23"},"1 Ne. 22:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/26.6"},"2 Ne. 26:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.24"},"D&C 101:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.3a","order":"02.37.001.62450"},["b","3a"],["span.small","OR"],"idols.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.19"},"Ezek. 7:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.4a","order":"02.37.001.62452"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/19.21"},"2 Ne. 19:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.4b","order":"02.37.001.62454"},["b","4b"],["span.small","OR"],"idolatrous priests."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.5a","order":"02.37.001.62456"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/23.12"},"2 Kgs. 23:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.13"},"Jer. 19:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.5b","order":"02.37.001.62458"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/11.33"},"1 Kgs. 11:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.6a","order":"02.37.001.62460"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/11.10.9-10"},"Jer. 11:10 (9–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.7a","order":"02.37.001.62462"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hab/2.20"},"Hab. 2:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.7b","order":"02.37.001.62464"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/day-of-the-lord"},"TG Day of the Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.8a","order":"02.37.001.62466"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/8.36.36-37"},"Morm. 8:36 (36–37)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.9a","order":"02.37.001.62468"},["b","9a"],["span.small","OR"],"over; i.e., to plunder and pillage."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.10a","order":"02.37.001.62470"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/33.14"},"2 Chr. 33:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.10b","order":"02.37.001.62472"},["b","10b"],["span.small","IE"],"the second quarter, a district of Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.11a","order":"02.37.001.62474"},["b","11a"],["span.small","IE"],"a district of Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.12a","order":"02.37.001.62476"},["b","12a"],["span.small","OR"],"complacent, indifferent."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.12b","order":"02.37.001.62478"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/48.11"},"Jer. 48:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.12c","order":"02.37.001.62480"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/3.14"},"Mal. 3:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.13a","order":"02.37.001.62482"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.11"},"Amos 5:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.13b","order":"02.37.001.62484"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/28.30.30,39"},"Deut. 28:30 (30, 39)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.14a","order":"02.37.001.62486"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/4.5"},"Mal. 4:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/110.16"},"D&C 110:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.15a","order":"02.37.001.62488"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/world-end-of"},"TG World, End of"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.16a","order":"02.37.001.62490"},["b","16a"],["span.small","HEB"],["span.translit",["span.emphasis","shofar,"]],"or ram’s horn."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.16b","order":"02.37.001.62492"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.57"},"D&C 101:57"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.18a","order":"02.37.001.62494"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.19.19-20"},"Joel 1:19 (19–20)"],"."]]}
